<br>
What it comes down to is.. make that spawn in Sol B that's just a turn in, rare. make the RF is Skyfire need the turn in from the Sol B guy, but make it so the RF in skyfire is almost always up. Then there is no contest of who gets forces there to kill it first.. because only 1 group of people will have the rare from Sol B to turn in and spawn the dragon. The only other solution is to make the rest of the cleric epic harder so it can't be done in a day by a dedicated group or 2. <p><p><font color="#000080"><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=161609 "><u> Bruein Bartleby,</u></a>
